"version": "1.0.2",
"title": "8366: wisdom, source of human",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8366: wisdom, source of human",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>True wisdom belongs to God and may be given by him alone. It cannot be received by those who put confidence in worldly wisdom which is based upon human cleverness and insight without God's revelation and which will come to nothing.</p>\n<h2>True wisdom comes from God</h2>\n<h3>It is given by God alone</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job12:13\">JOB 12:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:3\">EXO 28:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:36\">JOB 38:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:26\">ECC 2:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:17\">JAS 3:17</a></p>\n<h3>It is received through God's word</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:7\">PSA 19:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:99-Ps119:100\">PSA 119:99–119:100</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:130\">PSA 119:130</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:5\">ECC 8:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:8-Jer8:9\">JER 8:8–8:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos4:6\">HOS 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:24\">MAT 7:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:16\">COL 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:15\">2TI 3:15</a></p>\n<h3>It is received through submission to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:33\">PRO 15:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:6\">ISA 33:6</a></p>\n<h3>It is imparted by God's Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:17\">EPH 1:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:3\">EXO 31:3</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:31\">EXO 35:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job32:8\">JOB 32:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:18\">DAN 4:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:14\">DAN 5:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:3\">ACT 6:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:10\">ACT 6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:8\">1CO 12:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:5\">EPH 3:5</a></p>\n<h3>It is given in response to prayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:5\">JAS 1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:9\">1KI 3:9</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr1:10\">2CH 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:3-Prov2:6\">PRO 2:3–2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:12\">DAN 10:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:9\">COL 1:9</a></p>\n<h2>The emptiness of worldly wisdom</h2>\n<h3>Worldly wisdom is foolishness to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:19-1Cor3:20\">1CO 3:19–3:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:13\">JOB 5:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:11\">PSA 94:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:21-Rom1:23\">ROM 1:21–1:23</a></p>\n<h3>God cannot be known by worldly wisdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:21\">1CO 1:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:16-Eccl8:17\">ECC 8:16–8:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:9\">ISA 55:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:33-Rom11:34\">ROM 11:33–11:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:17\">1CO 1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:4-1Cor2:5\">1CO 2:4–2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:11-1Cor2:13\">1CO 2:11–2:13</a></p>\n<h3>Worldly wisdom builds pride and false hope</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa47:10\">ISA 47:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:7\">PRO 3:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:12\">PRO 26:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:11\">PRO 28:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:21\">ISA 5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:23\">JER 9:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:231\">COL 2:231</a>CO <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:10\">4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:18-2Cor11:19\">2CO 11:18–11:19</a></p>\n<h3>Worldly wisdom will be confounded</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:14\">ISA 29:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:19-1Cor1:20\">1CO 1:19–1:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:12-Job5:13\">JOB 5:12–5:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:30\">PRO 21:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:11\">ISA 19:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:25\">ISA 44:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:57\">JER 51:57</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:6-Ezek28:7\">EZK 28:6–28:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:17\">EZK 28:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:25\">1CO 1:25</a></p>\n<h2>The revelation of divine wisdom</h2>\n<h3>It is revealed in Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:23-1Cor1:24\">1CO 1:23–1:24</a></strong> <em>God's wisdom, which is hidden from those who rely on human wisdom, is the message of Christ crucified.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:30\">1CO 1:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:6-1Cor2:8\">1CO 2:6–2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:15-Col1:17\">COL 1:15–1:17</a></p>\n<h3>It is rejected by the worldly-wise</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:14\">1CO 2:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:18\">1CO 1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:22-1Cor1:23\">1CO 1:22–1:23</a></p>\n<h3>It is revealed to the unlearned</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:25\">MAT 11:25</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:21\">LUK 10:21</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:18\">1CO 3:18</a></strong> <em>God's wisdom may be received only by those willing to give up all reliance on their own human insight and understanding.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:26-1Cor1:27\">1CO 1:26–1:27</a></p>\n<h3>It is revealed through the church</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:10\">EPH 3:10</a></strong></p>\n<h3>God-given wisdom is superior to worldly wisdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:15\">LUK 21:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:15\">GEN 41:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:11-Exod7:12\">EXO 7:11–7:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:30\">1KI 4:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan1:20\">DAN 1:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:7\">DAN 5:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:10\">ACT 6:10</a></p>",
